{% comment %}
  PostureTru About Us Page Template
{% endcomment %}

<!-- About Hero Section -->
<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">{{ page.title | default: 'About PostureTru' }}</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; color: var(--color-text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      The story behind our mission to help you feel better, move better, and live better.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- About Content Section -->
<section class="section-padding">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
    
    <!-- Opening Section -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px;">The Way You Carry Yourself Changes Everything</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        My name is Kartik Sachdeva, and I founded PostureTru because of a belief that has shaped my own life:
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 16px; background-color: var(--color-bg); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);">
        The way you carry yourself affects far more than the way you look. It affects the way you feel, think, move, and show up in the world.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Like many people, I spent years sitting for long hours, working behind screens, and developing habits that slowly pulled my posture in the wrong direction. At first, it seemed insignificant. A little slouching here. A little neck strain there.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        But over time, I began noticing something deeper.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        When my posture was poor, I felt less energetic. Less confident. Less present.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        And when I stood taller, everything changed.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        I walked into rooms differently. I communicated more confidently. I felt stronger, more focused, and more aligned with the person I wanted to become.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        That's when I realized something I wish more people understood:
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Body Investment Section -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px;">Your Body Is Your Longest Investment</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We spend years investing in our education.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We invest in our careers.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We invest in our businesses, our homes, and our future.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Yet many of us neglect the one asset that stays with us for every second of our lives: our body.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Unlike almost everything else we own, our body cannot be replaced.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        The quality of our movement, our health, our confidence, and our daily experience of life are all connected to how well we take care of it.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Posture may seem like a small thing, but small things repeated every day become the foundation of who we are.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Posture Matters Section -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px;">Why Posture Matters</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Good posture isn't about looking perfect.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        It's about feeling capable.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        It's about moving through life with confidence.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        It's about reducing the physical stress created by modern lifestyles and becoming more aware of how we treat our bodies.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        When you improve your posture, you're not just changing the position of your shoulders or spine.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        You're changing the signals you send to yourself.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        You begin to feel more alert.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        More confident.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        More intentional.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        And those small improvements often ripple into every area of life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Why I Created PostureTru Section -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px;">Why I Created PostureTru</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 16px; background-color: var(--color-bg); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);">
        To help people build better posture habits and become more confident versions of themselves.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We live in a world where most of us spend hours every day sitting at desks, looking down at phones, and working in positions our bodies were never designed to maintain.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        The result is a growing epidemic of poor posture, discomfort, and physical habits that gradually affect our quality of life.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        PostureTru exists to help reverse that trend.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Our products are designed to support awareness, consistency, and healthier daily habits so people can feel stronger, stand taller, and live with greater confidence.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- More Than a Brand Section -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px;">More Than a Brand</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        PostureTru isn't just about posture correction.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        It's about self-improvement.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        It's about taking ownership of your health.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        It's about understanding that lasting change often starts with small daily actions.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Every day you choose to take better care of yourself, you are investing in the person you will become tomorrow.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        That philosophy is at the heart of everything we do.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Beliefs Section -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px;">
      <h2 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 32px;">Our Core Beliefs</h2>
      
      <div style="background-color: var(--color-bg); padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Your body is your longest investment.</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0;">
          The choices you make today shape how you feel years from now.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-bg); padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Small improvements create extraordinary results.</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0;">
          Consistency beats perfection every time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-bg); padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Confidence begins with how you carry yourself.</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0;">
          Posture influences not only appearance but presence, energy, and self-belief.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: var(--color-bg); padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Health should be practical.</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0;">
          Simple habits, applied consistently, can transform lives.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Thank You Section -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 48px; padding: 32px; background-color: var(--color-primary); color: white; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px; color: white;">A Personal Thank You</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        If you've found your way here, thank you.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Whether you're looking to improve your posture, reduce daily discomfort, build healthier habits, or simply feel more confident in your own skin, I'm grateful you've chosen to spend part of your journey with us.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        PostureTru was built with a genuine desire to help people feel better, move better, and live better.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Because when you stand taller, you don't just change your posture.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 600;">
        You change the way you experience life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Signature -->
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 8px; font-style: italic;">
        — Kartik Sachdeva
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-text); font-weight: 600;">
        Founder, PostureTru
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Page",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
